[
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘聽施經",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "東晉天竺三藏曇無蘭譯",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聞如是：一時，佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。時",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有一比丘，到講堂諸比丘所言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「諸賢者！",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今我不可經法，大著睡眠，不樂道行，疑諸經法。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」座中有一比丘，即行白佛：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a12_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「有一比丘，字聽施，來到講堂，謂諸比丘言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a13_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『今我不可經法，大著睡眠，不樂道行，疑諸經法。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a14_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」佛便報言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是比丘癡，不守諸根門，不少食，不上夜、後夜警順行，不觀諸善法，如是，當那可經法，離睡眠，樂道行，不疑諸經法？",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聽施終不從此得是。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言比丘：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「以不守諸根門，不少食，不上夜、後夜警順行，不觀諸善法，彼當那可經法，離睡眠，樂道行，不疑諸經法，終不從此得是。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a21_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若比丘守諸根門，少食，上夜、後夜警順行，觀諸善法，便可經法，離睡眠，樂道行，不疑諸經法，從是可得此。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a24_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告比丘：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「便呼聽施來。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a25_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」比丘便起，頭面禮佛足，往呼聽施。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聽施即至佛所，頭面禮佛足已就座，佛便言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a27_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「聽施！",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝所欲，便說之。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a27_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」聽施言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a28_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「今身不可經法，大著睡眠，不樂道行，疑諸經法。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a29_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛語聽施：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772a29_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我欲問若事，隨若所以知事說之。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b01_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若寧知，貪色不離、欲不離、戀慕不離、慷慨不離、愛不離，以彼色別離時，便生他變——憂愁、悲哀、痛亂、意殟——殟有是無？",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」聽施言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是若干從彼有。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b04_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b04_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉！",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b04_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善哉！",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "賢者如是應。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聽施！",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如彼不離，若寧知痛痒、思想、作行、識，若人貪識不離、欲不離、戀慕不離、慷慨不離、愛不離，以彼識別離時，便生他變——憂愁、悲哀、痛亂、意殟——殟有是不？",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」聽施言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b09_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼有是。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉！",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b09_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善哉！",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b09_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "賢者如是應。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聽施！",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b10_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如彼不離，若寧知離貪色、離欲、離戀慕、離慷慨、離愛，以彼色別離時，不生他變——憂愁、悲哀、痛亂、意殟——殟彼有是無有？",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b13_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」聽施言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b13_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼有是。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b14_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉！",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b14_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善哉！",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b14_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "賢者如是應。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b14_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聽施！",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b14_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如彼離痛痒、思想、生死行、識，若不貪識，無有欲、無戀慕、無有慷慨、無有愛，以彼識別離時，不生他變——憂愁、悲哀、痛亂、意殟——殟寧彼有是無有？",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b18_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」聽施言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b18_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼有是。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b18_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b18_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉！",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b18_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善哉！",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是應。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b19_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聽施！",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b19_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛便告聽施：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我欲為若說經法，上亦善，中亦善，至竟亦善；",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b21_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具為若現道行至竟，但諸善善好，當聽之，持著意中。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b22_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」聽施言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b22_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唯諾。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b22_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「曾有二人，俱出在道，其一人曉道徑，其一人不曉道徑。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b24_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不曉道徑者，便往問曉道徑者言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b25_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我欲至某聚鄉郡縣國，願語我道所由。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』曉道徑者便言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b26_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『汝從是道，直右行前，當有兩道，捨左道上右道，直右行須臾前當見溪谷；",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b28_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "溪谷上亦當復有兩道，捨左道上右道，直右行須臾當見叢樹；",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772b29_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "叢樹上亦當復有兩道，捨左道上右道，直右行須臾稍稍便得若所欲至聚鄉郡縣國。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c02_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我上頭所譬喻說，當知是一切所說亦當諦觀此所說。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "上頭所說不曉道徑者，謂世間邪道，亦復謂諸所受邪者所說；",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c05_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "上頭曉道徑者，謂如來不著正覺，亦復謂諸所受正覺者。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「所說左道者，謂諸惡人三惡念——一者、欲念；",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、亂念；",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、賊害念——亦復謂邪見、邪念、邪說、邪意、邪行、邪方便、邪志、邪定。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c09_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「亦說右道者，謂三善念——一者、出家念；",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c10_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、不亂念；",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c10_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、不賊害念——亦復謂正見、正念、正說、正意、正行、正方便、正志、正定。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c12_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「所謂兩道者，謂人所疑；",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所說溪谷者，謂瞋恚；",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c13_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所說叢樹者，謂五樂：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、眼樂色，愛欲可以好色貪著；",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c14_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、耳樂聲；",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c15_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、鼻樂香；",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c15_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、舌樂味；",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c15_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、身樂細軟，愛欲可以好色貪著。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c16_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所說聚鄉郡縣國者，謂無為德。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c17_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告聽施：",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是諸佛事，我以悲心故說是，其欲度脫者，我已愍傷之。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c18_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今彼是若事，當以寂靜樹下空閑一處，一心體行；",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若山澤塚間，當以果蓏為食。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c20_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘莫貪欲，於世間居後悔之。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c21_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是諸佛行，亦諸佛教。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」今佛已說，是賢者聽施便歡喜，思惟佛所說。",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘聽施經",
        "from": "T14n0504_001:0772c24_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]